    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-09-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-09-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="725" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d725">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Baron
                                    <persName type="to">Saurma</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-09-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 22,
                                    1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Excellency</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that
                            the President has appointed Mr. William Lea Chambers, of Alabama, United
                            States land commissioner in Samoa in place of Mr. E. J. Ormsbee,
                            resigned.</p>
                <p>Mr. Chambers expects, upon confirmation, to leave the United States for
                            his post about the 20th of October next.</p>
                <p>Accept, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Alvey A. Adee</hi>,<lb/>
                        <hi rend="italic">Acting Secretary.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
